content: [TextBlock(text="[2025 | Age 22] Just touched down in the concrete jungle of NYC, leaving behind the serene chaos of Tokyo. The skyline here looks different now, a bit more like the digital art I've been sketching lately. Japan taught me to embrace the unexpected and the beauty in imperfection. Now, back to the XVI ecosystem, but with a new perspective on life. #DigitalArtJourney", type='text')]
